  "text": "Found 6 deprecated classes in the Apache Flink DataStream API under flink-streaming-java/src/:\n\n1. **AscendingTimestampExtractor** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java, line 37): A timestamp assigner and watermark generator for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. No specific replacement is mentioned in the javadoc.\n\n2. **TextInputFormat** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java, line 37): An input format for reading text files. According to the deprecation javadoc: \"If you want to read/write data from/to text file, please use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. This class should be removed if we drop the supports for read/write via input/output format in DataStream api.\"\n\n3. **TextOutputFormat** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java, line 42): A FileOutputFormat that writes objects to a text file. According to the deprecation javadoc: \"If you want to read/write data from/to text file, please use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. This class should be removed if we drop all supports for InputFormat and OutputFormat.\"\n\n4. **OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness** (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java, line 56): A test harness for testing OneInputStreamTask. Recommended replacement: \"Please use StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder. Do not add new code using this test harness.\"\n\n5. **StreamTaskTestHarness** (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/StreamTaskTestHarness.java, line 101): A test harness for testing StreamTask. Recommended replacement: \"Please use StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder. Do not add new code using this test harness.\"\n\n6. **TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness** (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java, line 56): A test harness for testing TwoInputStreamTask. Recommended replacement: \"Please use StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder. Do not add new code using this test harness.\"\n\nThe deprecated classes fall into three categories: timestamp extractors, I/O format classes (legacy), and test harnesses. The I/O format classes (TextInputFormat and TextOutputFormat) are located in the legacy.io package and should be replaced with FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. The test harnesses (OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness, StreamTaskTestHarness, TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness) should be replaced with StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder."
}

